  Text: |-
    Snap ML Pool 
    
    In this example, see how using SnapML you can detect a real pool table with all 16 balls and pocket holes.  Step 1. Make sure you can visualize pool table and the white tracking circles in the editor, it won't need to match perfectly 
    
    Step 2. Build on Device and use a real Pool Table to track the balls
